            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A Good Snowman is Hard to Build",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has a very relaxing soundtrack, keeping you calm and focused on the task at hand. Completing this game will unlock new sections of the garden, expanding the areas you can explore and giving you access to more puzzles and wonderful melodies. There are also plenty of cute little interactions that you can perform, such as hugging the snowmen, leaning against hedges or sitting on benches, to name a few. Doing these will also change the music, which is a nice touch.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
